layout.p:
Columns: 12;
                                                  ruled lines: 40;
                                                  written lines: 40; Uniform layout. Ruling by hard point,
membrane by membrane. Visible pricking for ruling. Three to four columns per membrane.   Three tagin on most of שעטנזגץ, and one on בדהיחק; the letter ח arched throughout. Several majuscular and minuscular letters. The names of the sons of Haman arranged in 11 lines, in accordance with the rule.
